' /* dset_kbd_report
'------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Post a ControlWrite() request to the host that will perform the HID-specific
' HID_SET_REPORT function to set keyboard CapsLk, ScrLk and NumLk indicators.
'------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' On entry:
